      "text": "Now I have a clear picture of what needs to be done. There are three TODOs to fill in:\n\n1. **Bounds3::IntersectP** - Ray-bounding box intersection test\n2. **BVHAccel::getIntersection** - BVH traversal to find closest intersection\n3. **Renderer::Render** - Generate primary rays and cast them using scene.castRay\n\nAlso, the `Triangle::getIntersection` has an incomplete TODO. And the renderer needs to output PNG (currently only outputs PPM).\n\nLet me also check the context versions for any differences, and look at the PA6 PDF for more details:",
      "mediaUrl": null
