      "mediaUrl": null
    },
    {
      "text": "The image looks good — we can see the bunny rendered with proper lighting from two light sources, with the characteristic blue-sky background. The BVH acceleration is working correctly since the rendering completed quickly.\n\nLet me do a final check that all deliverables are in place:",
      "mediaUrl": null
    },
    {
      "text": "All deliverables are in place. Let me also verify a clean rebuild works from scratch:",
